when forecast earthquake , ENT_amr-unknown-0 do it happen that only a few case be successful while most case be failure ?
accord to this writer 's many year of research on precursory sign , the existence of precursory sign and earthquake prediction be -CONST--0 issue that be both connect and mutual differentiate .
the appearance of a precursory sign do n't mean it can accurately forecast the -CONST--0 element of an earthquake , because precursory sign be extremely complicate .
there be certain difference in the category , breadth , distribution range , and duration of precursory sign of different type of earthquake in different place .
in " NE_publication-0 , " this writer divide earthquake into -CONST--0 major type accord to the overall characteristic of pre @-@ earthquake sign : strike @-@ type and slip @-@ type earthquake .
the former occur in area where internal fault block or fault line converge but not intersect , while the latter occur in active fault line .
strike @-@ type earthquake have various type of precursory sign , which be widespread , long @-@ last , and quite variable .
slip @-@ type earthquake have fewer type of precursory sign , which have a smaller distribution range , short duration period , and smaller range of change .
