nuclear reactor process --
-CONST--0 meter fuel rod contain uranium oxide be burn to initiate fission -- the nucleus of the uranium atom be split , release neutron that collide with other atom , create more neutron in a chain reaction .
fission produce immense heat which be apply to water to create steam which drive turbine to generate electricity .
